org.nasdanika.html.model.bootstrap

Interface BootstrapPackage.Literals

  • Enclosing interface:
    BootstrapPackage

    public static interface BootstrapPackage.Literals
    Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each operation of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
